name: Gacofse
description:
Gacofse - Game about collecting of falling space eggs

You drive your space tractor and collects falling space eggs on your planetoid. There are 2 colors of eggs: red and blue. Each belongs to different container. Guess what!? Also red and blue. How many eggs can you collect within 5 minutes?

Controls:

wasd - driving tractor

mouse - selecting direction
